					<li id="email"><a href="mailto:?subject=Acquiring language proficiency&body=Hi%20There,%0D%0ACheck%20out%20this%20article%20on%20The%20Cavalier%20Daily%20-%20http://cav.stage.getsnworks.com/article/2014/09/language-competency-requirements"><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i><span class="hidden-xs">Email</span></a></li>
